Game: individual node process with its own ws server running.

ul.li:
(clone and run locally react app locally). Assume user is writing a bot in node:
User written bots exist in a subdirectory within the react application. An interface is provided in the browser to join a game and select which bot to run in the lobby. React makes the request for the WS url from the API, updates the endpoints, starts the bot.
